# ── TouchGFX ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ignore generated GUI code (Designer regenerates it), but keep the text
# database which we hand-edit to add wildcard resources and fix alignments.
firmware/TouchGFX/generated/**
!firmware/TouchGFX/generated/texts/
!firmware/TouchGFX/generated/texts/**
firmware/TouchGFX/build/

